snippet.title: Ripper - Video Game Trailer Long Version (1996) PC MS-DOS
snippet.description:
Ripper : video game trailer (long version).
Developed by Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc.
Published by Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc. in 1996 for PC (MS-DOS) and Macintosh in North America. Published in Europe by Gametek for MS-DOS.
Year : 1996
System : PC (MS-DOS) and Macintosh.

This trailer is what is played when you launch the 'non interactive demo' of the game.
